title: Bring your family home! Res Lease in Austin. 5 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: You must see this gorgeous 2-story, 5 bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home in Northwest Austin, TX just waiting for you!!
Such an amazing floorplan, this home welcomes you with a spacious living area filled with tons of natural light that makes the home so warm and inviting.

The well-designed kitchen is fully equipped with everything the family chef requires: ample counter space, plenty of storage in the pantry, and wood cabinetry, plus stainless appliances that include the refrigerator, gas range, microwave, and dishwasher.
All 5 bedrooms have carpeted flooring, ceiling fans and a walk-in closet.
The main bedroom has an amazing window placement, with a full bathroom, double vanity, walk-in shower and an amazing garden tub perfect to relax after a long day.
If all that isn't enough, this home also offers a 2 car attached garage and laundry room with washer and dryer units included.
Check out the private fenced backyard, ideal for enjoying family time or having friends over!
